name: Bee #Tiny
description:
SPECIAL MULTIPLE EDITION THEMED BEE
Bee collectibles based on actual bee species. Diversifying the collective idea of how bees look like and showing some of the bees that need saving. Every bee comes with a background that shows weather they are social, solitary or cuckoo bees and stats indicating weather they sting or produce consumable honey. Holographic backgrounds are super #RARE!...because they are endangered.
